Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:35.76,TITLE,,0,0,0,,恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,TITLE,,0,0,0,,第21话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,TITLE,,0,0,0,,死线

